      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable daily driver! This vehicle is in honest, fair condition, showing some expected wear and character from its time on the move, but it remains a solid and reliable choice. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a functional car with plenty of life left and a great personality!",
